        "text": "This whimsical vehicle carries a small number of passengers and crew. It\u2019s capable of short bursts of flight, but the weight of the clockwork mechanisms prevents sustained use. The pilot, crew, and passenger all ride on the back, straddling the hull on built-in saddles.",
