                    "type": "stat_block_section",
                    "subtype": "ability",
                    "name": "Wind-Up",
                    "ability_type": "offensive",
                    "text": "10-minute wind, 10-minute operation, DC 26, standby; Like all clockwork vehicles, a clockwork bumblebee must be wound up in order to operate, and a creature can decrease the operation time by 10 minutes with a successful Disable Device check at the listed DC. A clockwork vehicle can be placed into standby mode by its pilot as a 3-action activity. Its operational time doesn't decrease in standby. You can find more info in the wind-up entry here.",
